                        <interp inst="t18411025-name-267" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CHIVERS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a tailor, and live at Eaton. The prisoner was in my lervice, but left me on Saturday the 21st of August—I did not au<lb></lb>thorise him to get any goods for me, either when he was in my service, or afterwards—this order is not my writing—the whole of it is the prisoner's writing—I have seen him write when in my service—(<hi rend="italic">read.</hi>)</p>
